Description: Papyrus; Hieratic epistolary text recto and verso. Late Ramesside Letter (unnumbered), from Dhutmose to Bakenmut, Butehamun and Kar, requesting a letter.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (139342) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/139342)
